561f95c405734d8488ed8dcc8980d599.background: Wanna hear a joke? Thinking you have limits. I teach for that moment when you realize what I've known from the start: you can do this, and you're stronger than you know.
561f95c405734d8488ed8dcc8980d599.bio: Hannah grew up in Portland, Oregon and came to New York City to dance. She is passionate about guiding others’ fitness journeys and watching them evolve. A kick-your-butt drill sergeant, fiery New York dancer and a West Coast flower child all at once, Hannah is dedicated to a teaching style that empowers people to appreciate how strong they are, and how to protect that strength with stretching when they hop off the Bike and head out into the world.
ordered_q_and_as: Treat your body like it belongs to someone you love. Admire your strength, and take time to recover. And always ask yourself, #didyoustretchtho?
I'm on a quest to hang upside down from every ceiling on silks, hug every tree in the Northeast, and dance down every street in Manhattan.
561f95c405734d8488ed8dcc8980d599.quote: You are a rockstar. Treat yourself accordingly.
561f95c405734d8488ed8dcc8980d599.short_bio: "You are a rockstar. Treat yourself accordingly."

c0a9505d8135412d824cf3c97406179b.background: I have been dancing since a very young age, so expressing myself unapologetically through music and movement is second nature. I can’t wait to channel this energy and connect with you in this way on the Bike.
c0a9505d8135412d824cf3c97406179b.bio: Leanne is a former professional dancer turned fitness enthusiast who is passionate about movement and self-expression. Leanne has danced since the age of 3, and has worked her way on stage with some of the best-known artists in the world like Taylor Swift, Kylie Minogue and Katy Perry. Leanne’s style of teaching motivates you to step up, and step outside of your comfort zone. She believes that growth comes from areas of discomfort, and through her guidance and support, she’ll get you to the finish line with a smile on your face. Leanne is based in the UK and teaches live from our London studio.
ordered_q_and_as: I believe that music is what drives us, so I plan to curate meaningful playlists that will push and uplift you. I want you to feel supported but pushed so you get the most out of your time with me.

I love seeing new parts of the world, attending music festivals and rounding out my training through yoga and boxing. I’m always looking for a good piece of pizza or a green juice. Life’s all about balance!

048f0ce00edb4427b2dced6cbeb107fd.background: Sweat is the special sauce that bridges the gap between our inner and outer worlds. I approach every ride as an opportunity to change my life. We are transforming together, in real time.
048f0ce00edb4427b2dced6cbeb107fd.bio: Jess is a charismatic instructor with a boundless energy and passion for movement. With a background in dance, performance and fitness, Jess grew up down South and moved to NYC to commit to a career in wellness. Jess’s self-proclaimed sassy and spicy personality make her Bike and Tread classes uplifting and full of exciting surprises. Jess is committed to helping people heal from the inside out, and she believes that this community is the perfect place to start that journey. Her focus is to partner with motivated individuals looking to transform their lives — and together, they burn.
ordered_q_and_as: I lead from the perspective that you are whole now, and everything you need to get through the ride, your day, or whatever you’re confronting, is already inside of you.

I have a customized wellness transformation program called MindFULL3 centered around nourishment, movement and process. Through conversation and communal support, we help you design the life you were meant to lead.
048f0ce00edb4427b2dced6cbeb107fd.quote: I am the magma from the Earth’s core that ignites the fire of transformation in myself and others.
048f0ce00edb4427b2dced6cbeb107fd.short_bio: "I am the magma from the Earth’s core that ignites the fire of transformation in myself and others."
